des: This podcast discusses MedX Health, listed on the TSX-V under the symbol MDX, whose mission is to develop and implement non-invasive, practical, drug-free and cost-effective skin analysis and assessment systems for use by trained medical professionals, as well as light therapeutics and imaging systems that can help to save lives and enhance patients’ quality of life and improve standards of care.
